sources.title: Operation Delta Force 4: Deep Fault | Full Movie in HD | Explosive 90s Action!
sources.description:
Operation Delta Force 4 - A four-men Delta Force team is trying, with the help of a female scientist, to stop a mad terrorist who wants to detonate nukes in order to cause a massive earthquake. The team is out-manned and out-gunned, but has nothing to lose.
1999.  Stars: Greg Collins, Joe Lara, Justin Williams
